{"tid":1215231,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責警隊妄顧集體運輸上市民的公共安全","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:50:29.000Z","uid":119610,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"051624209f3a9a35b5bfcf86339183095b8d9a19","tid":1215231,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"警方警告市民：崇光外加入遊行對公共安全秩序構成嚴重威脅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1188429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1188429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n警方早前發不反對通知書，遊行須由維園草地出發；有記者問及，民陣引述警方曾稱維園草地可容納3萬人，警察公共關係科高級警司（媒體聯絡及傳訊）江永祥指，對有關講法「不太清楚」，僅指維園草坪達約1.4萬平方米，視乎人數密度，未能提供具體可容納人數。但呼籲參與市民勿互相擠迫，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「企得太密會對公共安全構成嚴重風險。」</span></span>警方又提醒，維園草坪是唯一起點，市民勿大規模在其他位置中途加入，會堵塞隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/337699/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B2%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E6%93%A0%E8%BF%AB-%E4%BC%81%E5%A4%AA%E5%AF%86%E6%9C%83%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F337699%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258B%25BF%25E4%25BA%2592%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2593%25A0%25E8%25BF%25AB-%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=35140985\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/337699/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B2%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E6%93%A0%E8%BF%AB-%E4%BC%81%E5%A4%AA%E5%AF%86%E6%9C%83%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA</a><br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n早幾日警方先講過「企得太密會對公共安全構成嚴重風險」，但今日又去港鐵使用武力強行推市民上接近爆滿的列車。要知道港鐵多條線路在繁忙時間的載客率接近、甚至超過100%［1］，今朝警察的做法無疑是「畜意令市民暴露於公共安全風險中，妄顧大眾的人身安全」，完全與警隊的使命相違背，社會各界理應予以譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［1］<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2051620/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B55%E6%A2%9D%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E7%B7%9A%E8%B6%85%E8%B2%A0%E8%8D%B7%E3%80%80%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%B3%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%88%97%E8%BF%AB%E7%88%86%E6%A6%9C%E9%A6%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2051620%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B55%25E6%25A2%259D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%25B7%259A%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%258D%25B7%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25A6%259C%25E9%25A6%2596&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=0e5ed7af\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2051620/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B55%E6%A2%9D%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E7%B7%9A%E8%B6%85%E8%B2%A0%E8%8D%B7%E3%80%80%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%B3%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%88%97%E8%BF%AB%E7%88%86%E6%A6%9C%E9%A6%96</a>"},{"pid":"4f1168cbb5e58d3de7f7f52658d562661d7d9671","tid":1215231,"uid":22894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:31:00.000Z","msg":"無論你搭咩車 點搭車 都要摸清楚緊急設備 <br />\n免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZ